  <summary date="2020-12-17T15:10:21Z" status="Introduced in Senate">EIDL Forgiveness Act

This bill modifies the loan forgiveness determination for a paycheck protection loan by excluding from such determination any advance amount for an economic injury disaster loan that was made to the recipient in relation to COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019).</summary>
